result.name: Dim Sum Deluxe

reviews.text: Great dim sum and great prices, really traditional and authentic compared to other dim sum restraunts we have visited. Excellent service too!
Dim sum there are tasty and size is enough for dinner.  Price is low.  Must try if you love Cantonese dim sum.

One of the best dim sum restaurant in Hong Kong.

All hand made dim sum. A small restaurant run by a young guy after 1980. It is located in a New Territories' shopping mall.

Their signature dish is shrimp dumpling in golden fish figure. The shrimps are al dente and fresh. Best food for IG to ask Like. Ha ha!

The scallop with rice vermicelli is very fresh and they put XO sauce on the top to make it more tasteful.

Pineapple cake is in a chick figure. The pastry is crunchy and the pineapple stuffing is soft and chewry. Its sweetness just fit.

The best dim sum I ever have!

really impressed with their effort to try something new, new cute idea for their dim sum
